snippet.title: WWE 2K15 - 2K Showcase Hall of Pain Trailer
snippet.description:
Relive the epic destruction that was Mark Henry's 'Hall Of Pain' in the new WWE 2K15 2K Showcase DLC! Available NOW for download on Xbox One and on 18th February on PlayStation 4!
